734757f-a.title: Brooklyn: Shore Boulevard - Exeter Street
734757f-a.text:
(1)
Bheepshead Bay, northwestward to Sheepshead Bay Road (note apartment
house thereon) from Shore Boulevard at Exeter Street.
July 13, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, showing a fisherman mending his nets in a close-up of
one of the fishing trawlers seen in the foreground of view No. 1.
July 13, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
